div.p:
And if men were so weak as of their own accord to offer it; can we think the Almighty Creator would accept of what was for it self only unbecoming his Majesty, and be so highly delighted with it, as to testify his Acceptance of Abel's by the descent of a Miraculous Fire to consume it;
〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉 . So Theodotion.
and to smell a sweet savour upon Noah's Oblation; to appoint it as a sign of his Covenant with Abraham; and lastly, to embody it into the Mosaical Institution?

I answer, They were of God's own Institution;
and therefore were received by the Patriarchs,
and accepted by himself.
